wbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ihClwsFiKu8o/v0/-1x-1.png" style="display: block; border-radius: 10px;" width="28" /&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;萨迪克·汗 (Sadiq Khan) 伦敦市长任期即将结束 10 周年。他亲眼目睹了这座城市受到英国脱欧、疫情和两次能源危机的影响。但这并没有阻止他实施任何城市中最严格的空气质量法规。但他尚未成功建造足够的房屋，并努力不断改善火车网络。随着城市的不断发展，汗与阿克沙特·拉蒂 (Akshat Rathi) 谈论了伦敦的成功和失败的教训。作为英国工党的杰出成员，汗也分享了他对该党未来的看法。采访录音于4月16日。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;立即收听，并在&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/DA6bwOIteV9JtHSx_bClbaTqoWtkhKYsVDwrjnpUBbFd5dNEeSZlKQBTtKeTwcjGy6y2fyBGCoDnYiafvA_DEGF9C4HAxZv97hIgRCiHEJyymj-1c_c5mnEniVy-eOWIY-HRoUT-yvA68RUf_7TST8jetpvyAkTKzfSDJ4tFPI1mz89tiCCP4Sgjyg1WQCYAatYUR4yl_Oi9eQf3ymFlfBuGVzVARbhHmxRh7rlmzbi67rN_5uSznxcfQ42EVMdRmGAYJGHg9Ge_ocIaLAZRWu6eZMoQvG1xcLdMXh_AZAMj06owH9qWFhw6INosrmdNyfDpUQ/Dn1tQnVlA30VMzqcfTkJfDDVp8vBAntE/20" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="零：气候竞赛"&gt;Apple&lt;/a&gt; 、 &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/YqOLSv62VWD_fsgKbXbxrHaiOqQa9vCXoZc8tqLNMwC21M3Bl-bsLpF1Gd4ZYku8wankc6dvNrFGoABSxqz7EqxbAgCfrQDhWZtR2J5LBhcNV3v-JX3jt43eOhUPerLLbNR6_yV4B7jW8kR_-0myyz68luZUKrZb-5TkAKfP_PGP4VuHiKSpjFxBoqGVPXFS9mEwb526FrmbB7MvGOsoTBQ_0A2jTUD_RR_ia2Hq88ucr4JoGr2V3NEfHRuyShNu2p_LztNv4idcJYNNOnxONs40JwMAVQpla1akYbwMmhR7hhUvJkH7UTKQcavyvhiG7gRbTBl5nAjbK9o-PkR1UDfaarJl/kKAqBz2fOXF_NaMMB2pmGsdiTzH0bIqR/20" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="零：气候竞赛"&gt;Spotify&lt;/a&gt;或&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/NVQvnspsXGE9Hxp3vb821j4RwgRTKYqwluro-fEG_IBP4S7cwNY1sJbrhF5ELSfqeZqjBObH1a9-A20EffuDB93YB0F5v2Xj4Jmzg1AHp5P0mzarBfaaFEmVuJm5qzhQz8GOgmIZ8jJWfdI6dcrrYgNL_KcmpF3SBCUFxoMpfrbt6Vpq6mvQ5pJDXol6l2EhczE47OcLfMhk6F7_40H8NNzYxPqWEGqmrGKqCWHYEPlWuWfJecB_NWA8mzTPmaZL0H8Gx0eXIBef15ASntBu1Krs6CDhzi0qHz4e4ICoou5xzc0IsPt-HcUBKXN0AmVzaw6XfzbxHWUtcJl_ToHiLkDizXpX/ZXLIhMLJey-QOvOR-XPD_Hte6WKH3eXc/20" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="零：气候竞赛"&gt;YouTube&lt;/a&gt;上订阅，即可每周四观看《零》的新剧集。 &lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2 style="font-size: 24px; line-height: 30px; font-weight: 700; padding-top: 12px; border-top: 1px solid; margin-top: 40px;"&gt;亚利桑那州的人工智能困境&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;作者： &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/5Njq9b18dFvFwstOyRtoX3hONFE_cHuJqMnJnK-nyXXo1eqdjAi3XNjBcmLbJhnl73JJOLfZgPxwoXAnMf8tnjc-LJy-E8xc9FyVXaO20wh8z-okuDrV7RBOhKevU8LQUy7a--gU6oyopl7vOFwh1e0tEvokgY98LO2Ba4jUk11iwys6KwhiDFaSYHbisQFJ9lrKxposVt8J5jdM2y042HsGV5M7h8uUm5EaCQYxjystxyBZZtnUPRVX_BBtLGGD-GHH24t5zRZMP-W6IWVl_vlKSN9xsC5n2VNrkiZHNP0pLFSvlPL5OCGchgC3QwfEwUJjDmg/eMOOz44xAXlX4boYWmrbAQj13LK9KaGn/20" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="托德·伍迪 |彭博社"&gt;托德·伍迪&lt;/a&gt;和&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/DTEsfdoppEl_YBzb8YYBccjFtlM7WkqSJMVOAV0S8R_aVx7dTfZYAI733Eu-IL14Mrpinyk5k8K_mL9Zj0jMDfCCH6o7xGqyHJgv7I6---0v1nnDwXUEgcoTeP3OxDnJeCtAwyUxDp0aUkpe2lXe3sTR13pCWGIKzmJutef4hFXAgZDFvGCJaIZm1Mr5CeaZkev4TqjxE0Z0CQyObILn1sdXVIAQsvUOHPFI5f9Xa92gYPYYQKhoU7UhQw-dTH6MwNR-R80_P3n3EP8Gp7965Io9OECoaHVuKDk5CK1WP-DEcx_Ev1qOadZ2Jxu4fjW10g699adzw_iraoeAsw/CELO7Dg9KrThZM6rbpB7wzBmudrnkex3/20" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="莱昂纳多·尼科莱蒂 |彭博社"&gt;莱昂纳多·尼科莱蒂&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;亚利桑那州依赖水&lt;strong style="font-size: 16px;"&gt; &lt;/strong&gt;为人工智能浪潮提供动力的数据中心正在迅速扩张——正如该州在&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/lUUabS_6grEyOx4VGDALGUNsHj6fUGPItZbOIqeJeo0-89WHnUcmO6YXQ7LFGH5qpdgiy2IoFVgGfeBLNwTaHeT77VwpUdeSqWv1qxSSecTwnxw7DGj18aGpoLhUHbzSuqUKeL2155PMMLJVhgEFPLJJEsuVfCIC3gqrfD7zHgHV_fwO641pRUaU_X_mffvZafhr-0LoCuVnfZHtGgac88At8Pmtb84hYrR179qiORx6SLHr4E_3K73fKmZw7x25moP7TmD0Sk2axVscnZYR3jo3MtFTutFSkcg94MfCKllLmArhCOFLLfOC_Z