r" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="技术深度"&gt;&lt;em style="font-size: 16px;"&gt;获取《Tech In Depth》时事通讯&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;em style="font-size: 16px;"&gt;，了解彭博社世界各地记者对技术业务的分析和独家报道。&lt;/em&gt; &lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2 style="font-size: 24px; line-height: 30px; font-weight: 700; padding-top: 12px; border-top: 1px solid; margin-top: 40px;"&gt;彭博社的新报道&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;&lt;em style="font-size: 16px;"&gt;即将推出：&lt;/em&gt; &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/iQEenGFORyShdZfYrZL0DPQsYRnptU6bdwdMcnfrpLuYmdKfxfEpIAhsrezW0ESnXHchU4AVKj5CfyPn3_cqXUA488pBpoZe7Wrc-91gvISyo71qh5Y0J9vJ4XJZd-oaC6TZXLwp0OCq6jLbT64fQN-n2p3qKR19lwH8uMeJlOwA5tM8g5bMh6p0tIG77TwBBO0sHdk0D2ChGvUgnpIFtVFfHIhjOQytmmbemfPr2rosIw_nge0QJrwXrDJj2wQTqLnPxoi3u0izJh4L-J5vShMQcbiwtCmS1DPuVqSZWpTvfDKsSw4r_7JhoVkJq1Aqpbj4/dLfsv-mqQ5h2QpCZ5I_g9my37EWnu3wU/20" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="今日人工智能"&gt;&lt;em style="font-size: 16px;"&gt;获取《今日人工智能》时事通讯&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;em style="font-size: 16px;"&gt;——通过彭博社全球新闻编辑室的分析，记录人工智能对企业、工人、政府和经济造成的破坏和威胁。&lt;/em&gt; &lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2 style="font-size: 24px; line-height: 30px; font-weight: 700; padding-top: 12px; border-top: 1px solid; margin-top: 40px;"&gt;本周游戏开启&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;杰森·施赖尔 (Jason Schreier) 在&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/VSFEUDYFQF9sHMtEgABcG-ACjbi8T3ipjToslZ-S6YlQ1Z59ugWdegUISav9iUxJSqhYk6_tsZzpUaAbeImd79_bnlV3KXXa6oJr_Z50w4k4pOLRT-G9IX0AwXxArkquTDHzsA6ROhdVn1mFmhAtaJYspjzEk6R_qjtRbSFX705bJ2ZNaT2Mfu7fsiT8tFvy74jqgxKmacZUmvrr2MkpGfR-1TH1CcUAMOCXsUzsReBgnXHAtU4C0mM_pj-AwIWyOghVNzrtsHog-Pq82SuRAOmx6Kj2Y8fM0hNzflJSHRlLv-d1x1-3ZzMC0A4e4O7HKmXsPJH19w-mv2xIPf71DlB0wP6sS2Mc3INc_GNrUmytN0bMVCSZMnnVcOGr0tJoUAAjnFgm0EdEucEkDPKLFjqfyv2qdq0aiHZlLcUAhB_O82-APXOmtZb7MUMA26usx_RLvkDUDazBT0uPEfALlmAMLLOcoydDmgP4qt6UsIoJwvRWJR1mWfBUvH1yiGhtcSgOswIpxlha-rM9JPY1YmRYYTdU7Ui