ant;"&gt;阅读更多&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style="border-top: 1px solid; margin: 24px 0 0 0;"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt; &lt;strong style="font-size: 16px;"&gt;Jane Street Group 去年创造了华尔街创纪录的&lt;/strong&gt;396 亿美元交易收入， &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/y5CdhPnbEpPgyX2yyw6iLrD7A79Ykl3vgIUIxq-ehVzU9lcX4K4bSmN0WUUqEVN_eWdOtgGpw2051cjKU5-j8JQtItGQLQwVyor5RrtvxbAIo-y-K_ByvYY2gncODAisMrY0reEZDAN1DkWg3MwQr7HnUdr4SBx0IAQkQyk9Lnfgd834C0iUmVSASldqnuFj99JDEf3VVLLtHSvTtnkEWeTatFWTRGzwSknSGhn2dQVCZwWKJc-8z4QpNzxz4iBP3Nf3yl-v9RRAgHla5J77F9IeGF8Q69epqlsOEgQ59yW3ZUAZgCXTJ_BvP5lxgXYhEPaSEbGElZ_5eLj_xXVk01NKoh2lpX1el2gzV4-CPiAGHT9vYe14cxFoRaWUFCW8GHGsZNUkArt2ZCJfnPvqK2RbqZZBbFEwrHBoJuTEf83o8i0KBNWze3ftrFvbUvvKrojbX1KV__yzro4hx2goZmOg6kUR8Z0IdWGk8E1qNMA9UeMtIN9MvOtYSkFPp_BD60rCBpoJK7E1YOnlCrCDmfcVBXmXHtTIfrusx7QjARYQy30/EP_0fSukRWUovDcDoOkg77cyKGyGeje9/20" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="Jane Street 以创纪录的 396 亿美元交易额夺得华尔街桂冠"&gt;令人惊叹地登上了行业顶峰&lt;/a&gt;。尽管只有 3,500 名员工，该公司仍以 11% 的优势领先最接近的竞争对手摩根大通。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt; Jane Street 的利润因其在私营公司中所持股份的估值飙升而得到提振，而该公司的主要业务——为不同资产的买家和卖家牵线搭桥——则在市场波动中蓬勃发展。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt; Jane Street 的增长在很大程度上依赖于技术和&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/yeAXoxT2pk7Pvp36YNxkgPnseEXyjicCfmIyaqNfrYpsT51XAynbpZh3aEN5CQEisaU_pg4p2zbUESB-tLjLi2id6uGgP58NDW-txlaE-jtGVUDZ-w6odpgRUmR-pkq5qRuO0jGmcSiSX6HJC7T3clvyFSbynoN434LFAb0wnfC0nTIb9gFh6bCaUfOpoVjiPqyjXBs3xKAba5cWDYOuJkUI1k-kcnTgrXb3LkMC569qapGHtyLDCqOQserXY8ZQi1XmYWf4h35zJfjzPHeRWvz0Bj_p8KlHNlFL33j3ul8U0gs9UrPFceoT_P9XZ1lzbpmo7WYtFnYNQAPsYDe87jB0wHBCNB7q6buZl7BZ9-yogbtGgrImTpQK81KL9Qdk8iof_jBB_8TkOorIcvDSdkVGbpuble3o5qOTu6sBIsDC-ZG0mJ4zSlGybiWjFddPbqaE8y_xfx7GusshxVWnfY8ig46-i8Fs6HEJWI3Hr4doWwi2EW61PR69lmgbqFfPrFxTzVSdnGJ_v3D25JI2gjcM09FrjJVMFtgE2s5b1Q/fH6Lyn2BaFQmrpZPpc2iU-Y-64Dd2ahg/20" rel="noopener nor